OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with Amy
OL,4,CDoherty's murder in Londonderry
OL,6,FA 30-year-old man has appeared in
OL,7,Fcourt charged with the murder of Amy
OL,8,FDoherty in Londonderry.
OL,10,FConnor McNamee, of Meehan's Terrace in
OL,11,FDerry is charged with the 28-year-
OL,12,Fold's murder on Saturday, with the
OL,13,Foffence said to be aggravated by
OL,14,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,16,FThe mother-of-two was found badly
OL,17,Finjured at her home in Summer Meadow
OL,18,FMews and died a short time later.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
