OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774634759
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with Amy
OL,4,CDoherty's murder in Londonderry
OL,6,FOn Friday, Mr McNamee was further
OL,7,Fcharged with possessing an offensive
OL,8,Fweapon namely a kitchen knife, as well
OL,9,Fas possessing class A drugs.
OL,11,FA police officer connected the accused
OL,12,Fto the charges.
OL,14,FThe accused appeared via video link in
OL,15,Fa wheelchair with visible bruising to
OL,16,Fhis face.
OL,18,FHe spoke only to confirm he understood
OL,19,Fthe charges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
