FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1774634759
OL,3,CMan appears in court charged with Amy
OL,4,CDoherty's murder in Londonderry
OL,6,FDefence solicitor Paddy MacDermott
OL,7,Fsaid that there would be no bail
OL,8,Fapplication.
OL,10,FHe said that this was "clearly a very
OL,11,Ftragic case involving the death of a
OL,12,Fmother of two young children" and said
OL,13,Fhe would be seeking a psychiatric
OL,14,Freport for his client.
OL,16,FDistrict Judge Oonagh Mullan gave her
OL,17,Fcondolences to the friends and family
OL,18,Fof the victim.
OL,20,FMr McNamee will appear in court again
OL,21,Fon April 23.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
